nhc_headline: ...GABRIELLE EXPECTED TO MOVE NEAR THE AZORES AS A HURRICANE IN A COUPLE OF DAYS...
summary: ...GABRIELLE EXPECTED TO MOVE NEAR THE AZORES AS A HURRICANE IN A COUPLE OF DAYS... As of 5:00 PM AST Tue Sep 23 the center of Gabrielle was located near 34.6, -56.2 with movement ENE at 21 mph. The minimum central pressure was 952 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 130 mph.
